'''康奈尔法学院法律信息研究所'''（{{lang-en|Legal Information Institute}}），英文全称Legal Information Institute at the Cornell Law School of Cornell University，简作'''LII'''，是[[康奈尔法学院|康奈尔法学院]]的一个[[非营利组织|非营利性]]的[[公共服务|公共服务]][[机构|机构]]，它提供免费的[[美国法律|美国法律]]和[[国际法|国际法]]研究资源的[[在线|在线]][[访问|访问]]，是在线提供[[法律|法律]][[信息|信息]]的[[先行者|先行者]]之一<ref name="MillerLaurence2001">{{cite book|author1=William Miller|author2=Helen Laurence|title=Academic Research on the Internet: Options for Scholars & Libraries|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=U3DTGfZkHywC&pg=PA160|date=19 March 2001|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=978-0-7890-1177-0|pages=160–}}</ref>。

该机构由[[彼得·马丁|彼得·马丁]]（Peter Martin）、[[汤姆·布鲁斯|汤姆·布鲁斯]]（Tom Bruce）于1992年创立<ref name='Amant'>{{cite book | last = St. Amant| first = Kirk | title = Handbook of Research on Open Source Software: Technological, Economic, and Social Perspectives | publisher = IGI Global | year = 2007| pages = 375 | url =https://books.google.com/?id=75KT6GdcWbYC&pg=PA375 | isbn = 1-59140-999-3}}</ref>，是第一个在[[国际互联网|国际互联网]]上开发的[[法律网站|法律网站]]<ref name='Laurence'>{{cite book | last = Laurence | first = Helen |author2=William Miller  | title = Academic research on the Internet: options for scholars and libraries | publisher = Routledge | year = 2000 | pages = 160 | url = https://books.google.com/?id=U3DTGfZkHywC&lpg=PA160&dq=%22legal%20information%20institute%22%20%22cornell%22&pg=PA160#v=onepage&q=%22legal%20information%20institute%22%20%22cornell%22 | isbn = 0-7890-1177-8}}</ref>。 

LII以电子形式在网上发布《[[美国法典|美国法典]]》、[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]的意见、《[[统一商法典|统一商法典]]》、《[[美国联邦条例法典|美国联邦条例法典]]》、若干《[[联邦规则|联邦规则]]》<ref name='Hart'>{{cite book | last = Hart | first = William |author2=Roderick D. Blanchard  | title = Litigation and Trial Practice | publisher = Delmar Cengage Learning | date = July 18, 2006 | pages = 160 | url = https://books.google.com/?id=P4ojyCvMbKoC&pg=PA24&dq=%22legal+information+institute%22+federal+rules&cd=25#v=onepage&q=%22legal%20information%20institute%22%20federal%20rules | edition = 6th | isbn = 1-4180-1689-6}}</ref>以及各种其他美国主要法律资料<ref name= Myers>{{Cite web
